{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "c1c7e6e4-aa4b-45ca-a1a3-9c10e3389462",
    "name": "Auth Code Flow + PKCE + PAR",
    "description": "Colección para simular el flujo de AUTH-CODE-APP-FRONTEND con Authorization Code + PKCE + PAR\n\n**HERRAMIENTAS AUXILIARES:**\n\n- `jwe-request-generator.html`: Genera el request JWE encriptado para PAR\n    \n- `oauth-browser-helper.html`: Asistente para completar el Paso 2 (autenticación en navegador)\n    \n\n**ORDEN DE EJECUCIÓN:**  \n0\\. Obtener JWKS (opcional, para referencia)\n\n1. PAR Request → Genera request_uri\n    \n2. Authorization Endpoint → Usar oauth-browser-helper.html\n    \n3. Token Exchange → Obtiene access_token\n    \n\n**REQUISITOS:**\n\n- Configurar mTLS en Postman (Settings > Certificates)\n    \n- Generar JWE con jwe-request-generator.html antes del Paso 1\n    \n- **IMPORTANTE redirect_uri:** Usa `https://localhost:8080/callback` o cualquier URI registrada en Keycloak. NO uses `https://oauth.pstmn.io/v1/callback` porque Postman oculta el código. Necesitas ver la URL completa con el parámetro `?code=` para copiarlo manualmente.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "17913263",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/17913263-c1c7e6e4-aa4b-45ca-a1a3-9c10e3389462?source=collection_link"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. PAR Request",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// Generar code_verifier aleatorio (43-128 caracteres base64url)",
              "const code_verifier = CryptoJS.lib.WordArray.random(32).toString(CryptoJS.enc.Base64url);",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('code_verifier', code_verifier);",
              "",
              "// Generar code_challenge = BASE64URL(SHA256(code_verifier))",
              "const code_challenge = CryptoJS.SHA256(code_verifier).toString(CryptoJS.enc.Base64url);",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('code_challenge', code_challenge);",
              "",
              "// Generar state aleatorio",
              "const state = CryptoJS.lib.WordArray.random(16).toString(CryptoJS.enc.Base64url);",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('state', state);",
              "",
              "// Generar nonce aleatorio",
              "const nonce = CryptoJS.lib.WordArray.random(16).toString(CryptoJS.enc.Hex);",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('nonce', nonce);",
              "",
              "// Timestamp actual",
              "const current_time = Math.floor(Date.now() / 1000);",
              "const exp_time = current_time + 300; // 5 minutos",
              "",
              "console.log('code_verifier:', code_verifier);",
              "console.log('code_challenge:', code_challenge);",
              "console.log('state:', state);",
              "console.log('nonce:', nonce);",
              "",
              "// IMPORTANTE: En Postman no se puede generar JWE fácilmente.",
              "// Debes usar una herramienta externa para encriptar el request object",
              "// o implementar la encriptación en Node.js con la librería node-jose",
              "",
              "// Payload que debe encriptarse como JWE:",
              "const payload = {",
              "    \"aud\": `https://${pm.collectionVariables.get('keycloak_host')}/realms/${pm.collectionVariables.get('realm')}`,",
              "    \"client_id\": pm.collectionVariables.get('client_id'),",
              "    \"scope\": pm.collectionVariables.get('scope'),",
              "    \"response_type\": \"code\",",
              "    \"redirect_uri\": pm.collectionVariables.get('redirect_uri'),",
              "    \"code_challenge_method\": \"S256\",",
              "    \"code_challenge\": code_challenge,",
              "    \"state\": state,",
              "    \"consent_id\": pm.collectionVariables.get('consent_id'),",
              "    \"authorization_details\": {},",
              "    \"prompt\": \"consent\",",
              "    \"nonce\": nonce,",
              "    \"exp\": exp_time,",
              "    \"nbf\": current_time",
              "};",
              "",
              "console.log('Payload a encriptar (JWE con RSA-OAEP + A256GCM):', JSON.stringify(payload, null, 2));",
              "",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('par_payload', JSON.stringify(payload));"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        },
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// Extraer request_uri de la respuesta",
              "if (pm.response.code === 200 || pm.response.code === 201) {",
              "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('request_uri', jsonData.request_uri);",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('expires_in', jsonData.expires_in);",
              "    console.log('request_uri:', jsonData.request_uri);",
              "    console.log('expires_in:', jsonData.expires_in, 'segundos');",
              "} else {",
              "    console.error('Error en PAR request:', pm.response.text());",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "urlencoded",
          "urlencoded": [
            {
              "key": "client_id",
              "value": "{{client_id}}",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "key": "request",
              "value": "{{encrypted_request}}",
              "description": "JWE encriptado - debes generarlo externamente con RSA-OAEP + A256GCM usando la clave pública de Keycloak",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "https://{{keycloak_host}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/ext/par/request",
          "protocol": "https",
          "host": [
            "{{keycloak_host}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "realms",
            "{{realm}}",
            "protocol",
            "openid-connect",
            "ext",
            "par",
            "request"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Pushed Authorization Request.\n\n**PREPARACIÓN REQUERIDA:**\n\n1. Abre `jws-jwe-par-request-generator.html` en tu navegador\n    \n2. Completa el formulario con los datos de esta colección\n    \n3. Usa los valores generados en el Pre-request Script (code_challenge, state, nonce)\n    \n4. Genera el JWE encriptado (RSA-OAEP + A256GCM)\n    \n5. Copia el JWE y guárdalo en la variable `encrypted_request`\n    \n\n**REQUISITOS:**\n\n- mTLS configurado en Postman (Settings > Certificates)\n    \n- JWE encriptado en la variable `encrypted_request`\n    \n\n**RESULTADO:** Obtendrás un `request_uri` para usar en el Paso 2"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Authorization Endpoint (Leer Docs - NO ejecutar desde Postman)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// Construir URL de autorización",
              "const auth_url = `https://${pm.collectionVariables.get('keycloak_host')}/realms/${pm.collectionVariables.get('realm')}/protocol/openid-connect/auth?client_id=${pm.collectionVariables.get('client_id')}&request_uri=${pm.collectionVariables.get('request_uri')}`;",
              "",
              "console.log('URL de autorización:', auth_url);",
              "console.log('');",
              "console.log('INSTRUCCIONES:');",
              "console.log('1. Copia la URL de autorización que aparece arriba');",
              "console.log('2. Pégala en el navegador');",
              "console.log('3. Autentícate en Keycloak');",
              "console.log('4. Serás redirigido a:', pm.collectionVariables.get('redirect_uri'));",
              "console.log('5. Copia el parámetro \"code\" de la URL de callback');",
              "console.log('6. Guárdalo en la variable de colección \"authorization_code\"');"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "https://{{keycloak_host}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/auth?client_id={{client_id}}&request_uri={{request_uri}}",
          "protocol": "https",
          "host": [
            "{{keycloak_host}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "realms",
            "{{realm}}",
            "protocol",
            "openid-connect",
            "auth"
          ],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "client_id",
              "value": "{{client_id}}"
            },
            {
              "key": "request_uri",
              "value": "{{request_uri}}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "**⚠️ PASO MANUAL - NO EJECUTAR EN POSTMAN**\n\n**Problema:** Postman no puede renderizar el formulario de login HTML de Keycloak.\n\n**Solución:** Usa `oauth-browser-helper.html`\n\n**Instrucciones:**\n1. Ejecuta el Pre-request Script para ver los datos necesarios\n2. Abre `oauth-browser-helper.html` en tu navegador\n3. Completa el formulario con los datos mostrados en la consola\n4. Sigue las instrucciones del asistente para obtener el `authorization_code`\n5. Guarda el código en la variable `authorization_code` de esta colección\n\n**Luego:** Ejecuta el Paso 3 (Token Exchange)"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Token Exchange",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', jsonData.access_token);",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', jsonData.refresh_token);",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('id_token', jsonData.id_token);",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token_type', jsonData.token_type);",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set('expires_in', jsonData.expires_in);",
              "    ",
              "    console.log('access_token:', jsonData.access_token);",
              "    console.log('refresh_token:', jsonData.refresh_token);",
              "    console.log('expires_in:', jsonData.expires_in);",
              "} else {",
              "    console.error('Error en token exchange:', pm.response.text());",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "urlencoded",
          "urlencoded": [
            {
              "key": "grant_type",
              "value": "authorization_code",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "key": "scope",
              "value": "{{scope}}",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "key": "code",
              "value": "{{authorization_code}}",
              "description": "Authorization code obtenido del callback",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "key": "redirect_uri",
              "value": "{{redirect_uri}}",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "key": "client_id",
              "value": "{{client_id}}",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "key": "code_verifier",
              "value": "{{code_verifier}}",
              "description": "Generado en el paso 1",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "https://{{keycloak_host}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token",
          "protocol": "https",
          "host": [
            "{{keycloak_host}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "realms",
            "{{realm}}",
            "protocol",
            "openid-connect",
            "token"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Intercambio del authorization code por tokens (Access Token, Refresh Token, ID Token).\n\n**IMPORTANTE:**\n- Requiere mTLS configurado en Postman (Settings > Certificates)\n- Debes haber obtenido el `authorization_code` del Paso 2\n- El `code_verifier` se usa del Paso 1 (PKCE)\n\n**Después de este paso:** Tendrás el `access_token` para acceder a APIs protegidas."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Extra. Obtener JWKS de Keycloak",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    const jwks = pm.response.json();",
              "    ",
              "    // Buscar clave para encriptación (use='enc')",
              "    const encKey = jwks.keys.find(key => key.use === 'enc');",
              "    ",
              "    if (encKey) {",
              "        pm.collectionVariables.set('keycloak_enc_key', JSON.stringify(encKey));",
              "        console.log('Clave de encriptación encontrada:');",
              "        console.log('kid:', encKey.kid);",
              "        console.log('kty:', encKey.kty);",
              "        console.log('alg:', encKey.alg);",
              "        console.log('');",
              "        console.log('Usa esta clave pública para encriptar el request object con JWE (RSA-OAEP + A256GCM)');",
              "        console.log('Puedes usar: https://dinochiesa.github.io/jwt/ o node-jose en Node.js');",
              "    } else {",
              "        console.warn('No se encontró clave con use=enc en JWKS');",
              "    }",
              "} else {",
              "    console.error('Error obteniendo JWKS:', pm.response.text());",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "https://{{keycloak_host}}/realms/{{realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/certs",
